r/Okafor.bio.html UConn bio]\n\n{{Navboxes|list=\n{{United States Men Basketball Squad 2003 Pan American Games}}\n{{2004 NBA Draft}}\n{{NBA Rookies of the Year}}\n{{2004 Connecticut Huskies men's basketball navbox}}\n{{NCAA Basketball Tournament MOP men}}\n{{NABC Player of the Year}}\n{{2004 NCAA Men's Basketball Consensus All-Americans}}\n{{NABC Defensive Player of the Year}}\n{{Academic All-America of the Year}}\n{{Men's Basketball Academic All-America of the Year}}\n{{Chip Hilton Player of the Year}}\n{{Pete Newell Big Man Award}}\n{{Footer 2004 Olympic Bronze Medalists Basketball Men}}\n{{Big East Conference Men's Basketball Player of the Year navbox}}\n{{NCAA Division I men's basketball blocks champion}}\n}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Okafor, Emeka}}\n[[Category:1982 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Nigerian men's basketball players]]\n[[Category:All-American college men's basketball players]]\n[[Category:American men's basketball players]]\n[[Category:American people of Igbo descent]]\n[[Category:American people of Nigerian descent]]\n[[Category:Basketball players at the 2003 Pan American Games]]\n[[Category:Basketball players at the 2004 NCAA Men's Division I Final Four]]\n[[Category:Basketball players at the 2004 Summer Olympics]]\n[[Category:Basketball players from Oklahoma]]\n[[Category:Basketball players from Texas]]\n[[Category:Bellaire High School (Bellaire, Texas) alumni]]\n[[Category:Centers (basketball)]]\n[[Category:Charlotte Bobcats draft picks]]\n[[Category:Charlotte Bobcats players]]\n[[Category:Delaware 87ers players]]\n[[Category:Igbo sportspeople]]\n[[Category:Medalists at the 2004 Summer Olympics]]\n[[Category:New Orleans Hornets players]]\n[[Category:New Orleans Pelicans players]]\n[[Category:Olympic bronze medalists for the United States in basketball]]\n[[Category:People from Bartlesville, Oklahoma]]\n[[Category:Power forwards (basketball)]]\n[[Category:Sportspeople from Houston]]\n[[Category:UConn Huskies men's basketball players]]\